data.description: All brick 4 bedroom, 2 bath ranch w/front porch. Family room has brick fireplace, built in desk and opens to an enclosed sunroom that is heated/cooled. Open eat-in kitchen has 1 yr new appliances, new flooring and coffee bar. Large Master suite has bathroom w/shower and sunroom is also accessible master. Check out the sizes of all the LARGE bedroom! Oversized 2.5 car garage  has newer insulated garage door, front and back access doors, heated/cooled. Concrete pad outside for RV, 200 amp electrical service, water heater 2019, full house attic fan. Garage has storage area above and has a 240 volt/30-amp electric receptacle. New HVAC in April 2023.
